Abduction of an American Playgirl has quite a bit of comedy between the sex scenes.  The story line is quite good for a sex film.  There is a good amount of sex which the abduters can't handle.  It hard to believe that one woman could wear out two men but that is what makes it so funny.

Admittedly, I am fairly stunned to discover CLASSIC 70's Adult films available on Amazon. The 70's were my High School & College years, and the women who participated in the films of that era played a major role in my personal sexual "awakening".......especially when there wasn't much sexual activity in my life (LOL). By the way.....Darby Lloyd Raines was a sexual BEAST! It's been practically 40 years since I first witnessed the talents of Ms. Raines on the big screen. It was my memory of her that lead me to purchase this DVD in the first place.
I think everyone should have a copy of this movie, the story was good, the picture was clear, and the acting was way above any level if we compare it with any other xxx movie.
